---
// /brands/viking-wall-oven-repair/ — C05 Wall Oven Batch 1
// VEWO + TurboChef Speed Oven + Tuscany. Middleby parts chain post-2013.
// Hub /brands/viking/ ✅. Tree P0 Luxury.

import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BrandBranchesGrid from '../../components/BrandBranchesGrid.astro';
import { MAIN_PHONE, MAIN_PHONE_TEL } from '../../data/branches';

const title = "Viking Wall Oven Repair | Southern California | VEWO, TurboChef, Tuscany";
const description = "Viking wall oven repair Southern California — VEWO built-in 30\", TurboChef Speed Oven, Tuscany. Middleby-owned since 2002. Greenwood MS parts. $89 diag. (424) 325-0520.";
const canonical = "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/viking-wall-oven-repair/";

const faqs = [
  { q: "What does VEWO mean on a Viking wall oven?", a: "VEWO is Viking's built-in wall oven product designation — Viking Electric Wall Oven. VEWO Series 30\" built-in single wall oven is the default Viking spec for LA kitchens that specified Viking during renovation work, typically alongside a Viking Professional 7 Series rangetop or range in the same kitchen. VEWO is positioned as Viking's wall-oven-category flagship — pro-grade engineering in a residential built-in form factor, with Viking's signature heavy-duty convection system and commercial-aesthetic design language. Double-wall VEWO configurations exist but are less common than single VEWO in our LA install-base observation. Service on VEWO runs through the Middleby Viking parts channel (Greenwood Mississippi distribution)." },
  { q: "Viking TurboChef Speed Oven — what's the service situation?", a: "TurboChef Speed Oven is Viking's microwave + convection + air-impingement combo — a built-in speed oven that cooks substantially faster than conventional ovens by combining multiple heat technologies. Viking licenses the TurboChef technology from TurboChef Technologies Inc. (a separate Atlanta GA company specializing in rapid-cook commercial ovens); the Viking consumer version integrates TurboChef's tri-heat capability into Viking's residential wall-oven column design. Service on Viking TurboChef: specialty parts chain (TurboChef-specific components run through both Middleby Viking + TurboChef Technologies distribution), longer lead times than mainstream Viking VEWO service (5-10 days typical on specialty TurboChef parts), and a different diagnostic approach than conventional wall oven. Common Viking TurboChef service: control-board lockouts requiring firmware reset, magnetron replacement on the microwave side, convection fan + element service on the thermal side." },
  { q: "Pre-2013 vs post-2013 Viking — does the Middleby acquisition matter?", a: "Yes — Middleby Corporation acquired Viking in 2002 but the quality-era distinction that matters for LA customers today is post-2013 refresh. Pre-2013 Viking residential (including wall ovens from that era) carried some quality-consistency issues that Middleby addressed systematically through 2013-2015 product generation refreshes. Post-2013 Viking VEWO and related wall oven product carries updated engineering, improved parts supply chain, and more consistent service experience. Pre-2013 Viking wall ovens still running in LA kitchens are serviceable — parts are still available through Middleby's Greenwood MS distribution — but the service economics on pre-2013 units sometimes favor replacement over major repair for expensive components like control boards. We verify production year at diagnostic and quote appropriately." },
  { q: "Viking Tuscany Collection wall oven — what's different?", a: "Tuscany Collection is Viking's heritage-European styling tier — same VEWO mechanical platform underneath, but with trim and design language pulling from Italian/European aesthetic rather than the pro-grade commercial look of mainstream Viking Professional. Tuscany wall ovens serve customers who wanted Viking's performance and build quality but didn't want the pro-kitchen visual in their dining kitchen. Service mechanics overlap VEWO mainstream — shared bake elements, similar control platforms with Tuscany-specific firmware variants, shared convection system. Specialty Tuscany trim parts (handle assemblies, panel finishes) run slightly longer parts lead than mainstream VEWO because the lower production volume." },
  { q: "Is Viking in the same corporate family as Wolf or Sub-Zero?", a: "No. This is a frequent LA customer question because Viking + Wolf are both premium US cooking appliance brands with overlapping luxury positioning, but the corporate structures are entirely separate. <b>Viking</b> is owned by Middleby Corporation (NASDAQ: MIDD) — a Tennessee-HQ diversified foodservice and residential appliance conglomerate that also owns La Cornue, AGA, Marsal, Evo, Viking Range + Professional + Tuscany. <b>Wolf</b> is owned by Sub-Zero Group Inc. — a privately-held Wisconsin luxury appliance manufacturer with sibling brands Sub-Zero (refrigeration) + Cove (dishwashers). The two corporations don't share parts, service networks, engineering, or technical conventions. Middleby Greenwood MS distribution handles Viking wall oven parts; Sub-Zero Group Madison WI distribution handles Wolf. LA customers with mixed Viking + Wolf kitchens run both parts chains independently." },
  { q: "What does Viking wall oven repair cost in LA?", a: "Residential diagnostic is $89, waived when you authorize the repair. Typical Viking wall oven service: VEWO bake element $380-$620; convection fan motor $420-$680; VEWO control board (current generation) $520-$840; temperature sensor $280-$440; door hinge $320-$520; door glass $440-$740; thermostat $340-$540; TurboChef magnetron service $380-$620; TurboChef control board (specialty) $680-$1,080; TurboChef firmware reset + diagnostic $220-$360; Tuscany trim-specific parts quoted individually; pre-2013 legacy Viking wall oven service runs roughly similar component pricing with longer lead times on specialty parts (7-14 days); double wall oven per-cavity service $420-$780. Middleby Greenwood MS distribution typically 3-5 days on common Viking service parts." }
];

const schemaJsons = [
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "LocalBusiness", "@id": canonical + "#business",
    "name": "Same Day Appliance Repair — Viking Wall Oven Service",
    "image": "https://samedayappliance.repair/images/same-day-appliance-repair.png",
    "url": canonical, "telephone": "+1-424-325-0520", "priceRange": "$$$$",
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ]
  },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "Service", "serviceType": "Viking Wall Oven Repair",
    "provider": { "@id": canonical + "#business" },
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ],
    "description": "Viking wall oven repair across LA — VEWO Series built-in 30\" single + double, TurboChef Speed Oven built-in, Tuscany Collection heritage-European tier. Middleby-owned since 2002; Greenwood MS parts distribution. Pre-2013 vs post-2013 generation awareness. $89 residential diagnostic waived with repair.",
    "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "priceSpecification": { "@type": "PriceSpecification", "price": "89.00", "priceCurrency": "USD", "description": "Residential diagnostic fee, waived with repair" } }
  },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "FAQPage", "mainEntity": faqs.map(f => ({ "@type": "Question", "name": f.q, "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": f.a.replace(/<[^>]+>/g, '') } })) },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Brands", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Viking", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/viking/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 4, "name": "Viking Wall Oven Repair", "item": canonical }
    ]
  }
];
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <Fragment slot="head-scripts">{schemaJsons.map((schema) => (<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />))}</Fragment>
  <div class="call-banner"><div class="wrap"><span>Viking wall oven service? Same-day across LA:</span><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="phone-lg">{MAIN_PHONE}</a></div></div>

  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › Viking › Wall Oven Repair</div>
    <h1>Viking Wall Oven Repair</h1>
    <p class="lede">Viking VEWO Series built-in wall oven (30" single + double configurations with Viking's pro-grade convection system), TurboChef Speed Oven built-in (microwave + convection + air-impingement tri-heat), and Tuscany Collection heritage-European tier — our techs service Viking wall ovens across LA, Orange County, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside. Viking is owned by Middleby Corporation (NASDAQ: MIDD, Tennessee HQ); manufacturing continues at Viking's Greenwood Mississippi facility; parts distribution runs through Middleby's Greenwood MS service infrastructure. Pre-2013 vs post-2013 generation-aware service approach. $89 residential diagnostic waived with the repair.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta"><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="btn btn-primary">Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a><a href="#book" class="btn btn-ghost">Request a Visit</a></div>
